{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We decided that we want to go to Israel, to Palestine, then, the two of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody-- my husband's sister, nobody else wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my husband was a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He felt very strongly about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He worked, already, before the war, with various of the youth movements.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as my father-- all I heard, throughout my childhood, Israel, Palestine, and you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would have loved to chuck it all in and go, instead of Krakow, to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was not a time, that was not-- where families sort of got separated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had a mother, you had-- anyhow, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So how did you get in touch with this group, Aliyah Bet?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- look, I-- this, I left for my husband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got in touch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- He-- all of those things, till he passed away, whatever it was, if it was something illegal, if-- if it was things, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took-- I took care of the home, of the hearth, and he took care of the mind, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As long-- as long as I-- as long as I could read, as I could study, as I could do things, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he always-- he was a man that didn't-- did this not only for his family but for a lot of-- if you would ask around, people in this town, they will let you-- they would-- they would let you know what he did.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you describe your journey to Israel?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was horrific, because we went to-- we literally walked to Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked, too, at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went to some-- through some lakes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we had some guides, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had some Jewish or Israeli guides.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
